editorial:
**Trick:** 0 → -1, 1 → +1. Equal counts means subarray sum = 0. Longest such subarray = max distance between two equal prefix sums.

**HashMap-Backed Sliding Window O(n):** Prefix sum maintain, har sum ka pehla index store. Same sum dobara mile to length = i - firstIndex.

```js
function longestEqualWindow(seats) {
  const first = new Map();
  first.set(0, -1); // empty prefix
  let sum = 0, best = 0;
  for (let i = 0; i < seats.length; i++) {
    sum += seats[i] === 0 ? -1 : 1;
    if (first.has(sum)) {
      const len = i - first.get(sum);
      if (len > best) best = len;
    } else {
      first.set(sum, i);
    }
  }
  return best;
}
```

**Time:** O(n). **Space:** O(n). Equal-element problems aksar prefix-sum-with-hashmap se solve hote hain — yeh 'extended sliding window' family ka member hai.

